HALJA

Controls:
	KEYBOARD
	=================================================================
	Up, Down, Left, Right - Move Entity
	I - View contents of your backpack
	
	W, A, S, D - Move tile marker (hold SHIFT for range selection)
	Z, X - Change tile
	DEL - Hide tile
	PGUP - Edit wall map
	PGDWN - Edit floor map
	
	F8 - Toggle exclusive layer mode
	
	F11 - Load previous save
	F12 - Save current world
	
	ESC - Exit to menu
	=================================================================
	
	
	MOUSE
	=================================================================
	Left click and drag to select a range of tiles
	Right click for popup menu to select tiles
	=================================================================